text: Fejér is an administrative county in Hungary. The capital of Fejér county is Székesfehérvár. It is in the central part of the country. The county borders with Bács-Kiskun, Komárom-Esztergom, Pest, Somogy, Tolna and Veszprém. It is near the Lake Balaton. In 2019, 417,712 people lived there. Its area is 4,358 km².
title: Fejér County
